OL,3,CWhat is happening in Mexico and what
OL,4,Cis the travel advice for Brits?
OL,6,FOne of Mexico's most notorious drug
OL,7,Flords "El Mencho" was killed in a
OL,8,Fmilitary operation on Sunday in
OL,9,FTapalpa, sparking widespread
OL,10,Fretaliatory violence
OL,12,FThe death of one man has triggered
OL,13,Fviolent protests across Mexico,
OL,14,Fforcing stern travel warnings for
OL,15,Ftourists in the country and casting
OL,16,Fdoubt over this summer's World Cup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
