OL,3,CWhat is happening in Mexico and what
OL,4,Cis the travel advice for Brits?
OL,6,FOn Sunday, El Mencho - Mexico's most
OL,7,Fwanted man - and six of his
OL,8,Facquaintances were killed during a
OL,9,Fmilitary operation in the state of
OL,10,FJalisco.
OL,12,FHis death triggered chaos in the
OL,13,Fcountry, with vehicles set ablaze
OL,14,Facross the state, including in the
OL,15,Ftourist hot spots of Guadalajara and
OL,16,FPuerto Vallarta.
OL,18,FWho is El Mencho?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
