OL,3,CWhat is happening in Mexico and what
OL,4,Cis the travel advice for Brits?
OL,6,FKnown as El Mencho, Nemesio Ruben
OL,7,FOseguera Cervantes, 59, was a Mexican
OL,8,Fdrug lord and head of the Jalisco New
OL,9,FGeneration Cartel (JNGC).
OL,11,FBorn in the state of Michoacan, El
OL,12,FMencho rose through cartel ranks after
OL,13,Fbeing deported from the US in the
OL,14,Fearly 1990s.
OL,16,FHe became infamous for sensational
OL,17,Facts of violence and his aggressive
OL,18,Fleadership of the JNGC.
OL,26,@nD@`rrsD@]rp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
