PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1771931090
OL,3,CWhat is happening in Mexico and what
OL,4,Cis the travel advice for Brits?
OL,6,FEl Mencho's JNGC was also allegedly
OL,7,Finvolved in the assassination attempts
OL,8,Fof Mexican government officials. The
OL,9,Fcartel is known for trafficking huge
OL,10,Fquantities of fentanyl and other drugs
OL,11,Finto the United States.
OL,13,FBefore his death, the US Department of
OL,14,FState had offered a $15 million reward
OL,15,Ffor information on the cartel leader.
OL,17,FUS prosecutors once accused JNGC
OL,18,Foperatives of bringing down a Mexican
OL,19,Fmilitary helicopter with a rocket-
OL,20,Fpropelled grenade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
