OL,3,CWhat is happening in Mexico and what
OL,4,Cis the travel advice for Brits?
OL,6,FIn 2020, the cartel carried out a
OL,7,Fspectacular assassination attempt with
OL,8,Fgrenades and high-powered rifles in
OL,9,Fthe heart of Mexico City against the
OL,10,Fthen-head of the capital's police
OL,11,Fforce and now federal security
OL,12,Fsecretary.
OL,14,FHow was El Mencho finally caught?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
