OL,3,CWhat is happening in Mexico and what
OL,4,Cis the travel advice for Brits?
OL,6,FAccording to the country's defence
OL,7,Fsecretary, General Ricardo Trevilla
OL,8,FTrejo, the military began an operation
OL,9,Fto arrest El Mencho, after which a
OL,10,F"very violent clash" between cartel
OL,11,Fmembers and Mexican special forces
OL,12,Fensued.
OL,14,FDuring the operation to capture him in
OL,15,FTapalpa, Jalisco, troops came under
OL,16,Ffire and killed four people at the
OL,17,Flocation.
OL,19,FFour more people, including El Mencho,
OL,20,Fwere wounded and later died, according
OL,21,Fto the country's defense secretary.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
