OL,3,CWhat is happening in Mexico and what
OL,4,Cis the travel advice for Brits?
OL,6,FTwo others were arrested, and armoured
OL,7,Fvehicles, rocket launchers, and other
OL,8,Farms were seized. Three members of the
OL,9,Farmed forces were wounded and are
OL,10,Freceiving medical treatment.
OL,12,FWhy has the UK issued a travel warning
OL,13,Fin Mexico?
OL,15,FThe Foreign Office has urged Britons
OL,16,Fto avoid unnecessary travel to the
OL,17,Fareas where the violence is happening.
OL,19,FIt advised those already in Puerto
OL,20,FVallarta to remain indoors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
