OL,3,CWhat is happening in Mexico and what
OL,4,Cis the travel advice for Brits?
OL,6,FMexico is one of three host countries
OL,7,Ffor the 2026 World Cup, alongside
OL,8,FCanada and the US. Guadalajara is one
OL,9,Fof Mexico's three host cities, along
OL,10,Fwith Mexico City and Monterrey.
OL,12,FIt is almost unprecedented for such
OL,13,Flevels of violence to occur in a host
OL,14,Fcity, just months before fans from
OL,15,Faround the world are due to visit.
OL,17,FGuadalajara is due to host a match on
OL,18,Fthe opening night of the tournament,
OL,19,Fas well as the highly anticipated
OL,20,Fgroup stage match between Uruguay and
OL,21,FSpain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
