CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1771931090
OL,3,CWhat is happening in Mexico and what
OL,4,Cis the travel advice for Brits?
OL,6,FNeither England nor Scotland will be
OL,7,Fplaying any of their matches in
OL,8,FGuadalajara. However, they could play
OL,9,Fin Mexico City should they reach the
OL,10,Fknockouts.
OL,12,FNo new travel guidance has been issued
OL,13,Ffor the tournament in response to the
OL,14,Flatest unrest.
OL,16,FHowever, the Foreign Office had issued
OL,17,Fadvice for Britons to stay safe while
OL,18,Fvisiting the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
